{
  "stem": "56.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and it became a big thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Almost everybody had someone in the family who was smuggling, someone who didn't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't take long for the Germans to get wise to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once they got wise to it, they started to check the people, who were walking near the fence, on the Polish side, for passports.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you didn't have a passport, they knew immediately that you were a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day, we were told that my sister was arrested.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my father went to the building where the Jewish people, who were in charge-- of the-- the Jewish police, already.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, yes, she is in this central place, which was called [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], which means [NON-ENGLISH] was the name of the section where the ghetto was.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] means a market, which was, before the war, but, at this time, it was a place where the Germans used to come in to ghetto through that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had like a compound there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- they stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all the business was transacted through this [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my father went-- we all went to see where she was and try to bring her home, which we did, because he had a little influence.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He knew-- a lot of people knew him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they released her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But she was so badly beaten, that she had to be brought home on a stretcher.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she proceeded to lay for almost three weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Her back-- this was the first time in my life I saw scars on someone's back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was just black.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was just raw, bloody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's how she ended her career as a smuggler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, it didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We ran out of food again.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
